      <h1>What is Luca?</h1>
      <p>Luca is a Layout framework for Backbone.js.  It is inspired by ExtJS, and from a years worth of experience in the trenches developing large apps with Backbone.JS.  In addition to providing many different types of nestable containers, which automatically handle rendering for you, it augments the Backbone.View class with many of the best practices I have learned.  It features things like lazy instantiation of views, a component type registry, a view cache, and many other things which I will document here. </p>
